* The [[sortby|sortby Operator]] filter operator now places input titles that are missing from the reference list after the listed ones, matching the documented behaviour; with a list `Alpha Beta Gamma`, the input `Delta Epsilon Alpha Beta Gamma` now sorts to `Alpha Beta Gamma Delta Epsilon` instead of leading with the unlisted titles (fixes [[Issue #8342|https://github.com/TiddlyWiki/TiddlyWiki5/issues/8342]])
